        if nums[i] % 2 == 0 and nums[i] % 3 == 0:
            print(nums[i])
            count += 1
        if nums[i] % 2 != 0 and nums[i] != 1:
            is_prime = True
            for j in range(2, int(nums[i] ** 0.5) + 1):
                if nums[i] % j == 0:
                    is_prime = False
                    break
            if is_prime:
                break
        i += 1
    return count
